approveWithdrawal(uint256).details: Approve a withdrawal after guardian review

blockWithdrawal(uint256).details: Block a withdrawal based on guardian decision

params._commitment: The commitment hash (hash of secret and nullifier)

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

publishAssociationSet(bytes32,string).details: Publish an association set for compliance

params._ipfsHash: IPFS hash containing the proof data
params._merkleRoot: Root of the association merkle tree

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. params._merkleProof: Proof of inclusion in the merkle tree
params._nullifier: The nullifier to prevent double spending
